articles.title: Australia to buy 3 nuclear subs under AUKUS pact: White House - Al Jazeera English

articles.content: The White House has announced that Australia will buy three American nuclear submarines under a new security pact with the United States and the United Kingdom. The statement comes ahead of a meeting… [+5243 chars]
